metadata.name: Underwater Fantasy
metadata.description:
Their eyes strained against the dark,
But suddenly, a spark!
A glow, so bright and bold,
It warmed their hearts and souls.
They watched in awe and wonder,
As creatures, luminescent and tender,
Swam around them, graceful and free,
In this underwater fantasy.

The humans were in awe,
As they watched these giants, without a flaw,
Dancing in the blackened depths,
As if performing for their guests.

Their colors were so vibrant,
Their movements so elegant,
And as the humans gazed,
They knew they had been graced.

With a once-in-a-lifetime sight,
In this world of darkness and might,
Where the deep-sea creatures roam,
And human explorers call home.
